Smart-Energy-Consumption-Forecasting-System/
├─ backend/
│  ├─ app.py                     # Flask API for forecasts and anomalies
│  ├─ lstm_model.py              # LSTM model for time-series forecasting
│  ├─ requirements.txt           # Python dependencies
│  └─ data/
│      ├─ sample_energy.csv      # Hourly meter energy readings
│      └─ anomalies.csv          # Detected anomalies sample
├─ frontend/
│  ├─ public/
│  │   └─ index.html             # React entry point
│  ├─ src/
│  │   ├─ App.jsx                # Main React component
│  │   ├─ ForecastDashboard.jsx  # Forecast panel component
│  │   ├─ AnomalyPanel.jsx       # Anomaly panel component
│  │   ├─ index.js               # ReactDOM render file
│  │   └─ styles.css             # Global CSS + Tailwind
│  └─ package.json               # Frontend dependencies & scripts
├─ README.md                     # Project overview and instructions
└─ .gitignore                    # Git ignore file
